eat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Delhi%20Police%20have%20traced%20the%20origin%20of%20the%20emails.%20I%20am%20assuring%20citizens%20of%20Delhi%20that%20the%20police%20are%20alert%2C%20getting%20leads%2C%20and%20will%20take%20strict%20action%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Saxena%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20took%20some%20time%20for%20the%20police%20to%20trace%20the%20email's%20origin%20as%20it%20was%20sent%20using%20a%20virtual%20private%20network%20(VPN)%20that%20routed%20and%20rerouted%20data%20via%20foreign%20servers.%20The%20police%20managed%20to%20narrow%20down%20on%20the%20internet%20protocol%20(IP)%20address%20-%20a%20unique%20identifier%20-%20after%20retracing%20the%20VPN%20traffic%20and%20found%20the%20source%20of%20the%20email%2C%20sources%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BToday%2C%20bomb%20threats%20have%20been%20received%20to%20some%20schools%20in%20Delhi%20through%20emails.%20Taking%20action%20on%20these%20threats%2C%20Delhi%20Police%20conducted%20thorough%20check%20of%20all%20such%20schools%20as%20per%20protocol.%20However%2C%20nothing%20objectionable%20has%20been%20found.%20It%20appears%20it%20was%20a%20hoax.%20Delhi%20Police%20request%20the%20public%20not%20to%20panic%20and%20maintain%20peace%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20police%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Delhi%20Police's%20Special%20Cell%20has%20started%20an%20investigation%2C%20though%20nothing%20suspicious%20has%20been%20found%20in%20any%20of%20the%20schools%2C%20the%20police%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe've%20checked%20all%20the%20schools%20and%20nothing%20has%20been%20found%3B%20there%20is%20no%20need%20to%20panic%2C%26quot%3B%20senior%20police%20officer%20Kumar%20Mahla%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Saxena%20said%20he%20has%20sought%20a%20detailed%20probe%20from%20the%20Delhi%20Police%20chief.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B...%20I%20request%20the%20parents%20not%20to%20panic%2C%20and%20cooperate%20with%20the%20administration%20in%20ensuring%20safety%20of%20schools%20and%20the%20children.%20The%20miscreants%20and%20culprits%20will%20not%20be%20spared%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Saxena%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20and%20fire%20department%20officers%20are%20conducting%20thorough%20inspections%20in%20all%20the%20schools%20that%20received%20the%20bomb%20threat%20around%204.15%20am.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20got%20information%20that%20the%20same%20email%20was%20sent%20to%20several%20schools%20at%20around%204%3A15%20am.%20We%20took%20action%20and%20decided%20to%20close%20the%20schools%20and%20send%20the%20students%20back%20home.%20Checking%20is%20underway%20at%20all%20the%20schools%20and%20our%20technical%20wing%20is%20investigating%20the%20email.%20Through%20the%20initial%20investigation%2C%20it%20seems%20that%20this%20is%20a%20mass%20email%2C%26quot%3B%20senior%20police%20officer%20Rohit%20Meena%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20asked%20parents%20to%20remain%20calm%20as%20all%20precautions%20are%20being%20taken.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDelhi%20Public%20School%20Noida%20principal%20Kaamini%20Bhasin%20said%20safety%20is%20their%20top%20priority.%20%26quot%3BWe%20received%20a%20mail%20regarding%20a%20bomb.%20We%20have%20students%20so%20we%20can't%20take%20the%20risk.%20We%20informed%20the%20police.%20The%20parents%20have%20been%20informed%2C%20and%20the%20students%20have%20been%20sent%20back%20home%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Kaamini%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714546380000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fivamst6_bomb-threat_625x300_01_May_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fdelhi-news%2Frequest-parents-not-to-panic-delhi-lt-governor-vk-saxena-on-bomb-threat-to-schools-5562794%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20national%20capital's%20Lieutenant%20Governor%20VK%20Saxena%20today%20said%20the%20police%20have%20traced%20the%20origin%20of%20the%20hoax%20bomb%20emails%20sent%20to%20nearly%20100%20schools%20in%20Delhi%20and%20the%20National%20Capital%20Region%20(NCR).%22%2C%22author%22%3