4423.cms%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETimes%20of%20India%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Pant%20went%20on%20a%20strict%20calorie%20deficit%20program%20for%20which%20he%20had%20to%20snub%20his%20favourite%20food%20items%20like%20fried%20chicken%2C%20rasmalai%20and%20biryani.%20But%2C%20he%20couldn't%20give%20up%20on%20chilly%20chicken%2C%20which%20was%20then%20prepared%20using%20just%205ml%20of%20extra%20virgin%20olive%20oil.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20adopted%20a%20calorie-deficit%20diet%20since%20late%20December.%20If%20his%20body%20demanded%201400%20calories%20a%20day%2C%20he%20was%20given%20around%201000%20calories.%20It%20was%20tough%20on%20him%20since%20he%20had%20to%20train%20very%20hard%20to%20gain%20match-fitness%20and%20had%20to%20strengthen%20the%20muscles%20on%20his%20injured%20right%20leg%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20source%20involved%20in%20Pant's%20rehabilitation%20told%20TOI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPant%20wanted%20flavour%20in%20his%20food.%20That's%20why%20he%20moved%20into%20a%20rented%20house%20in%20Bengaluru%20while%20he%20was%20at%20the%20NCA%2C%20instead%20of%20a%20hotel.%20He%20preferred%20home-cooked%20food.%20He%20was%20allowed%20only%205%20ml%20of%20extra%20virgin%20olive%20oil.%20He%20couldn't%20give%20up%20his%20love%20for%20chilly%20chicken.%20So%2C%20a%20recipe%20was%20derived%20to%20make%20it%20with%20that%20much%20oil.%20Goan%20bhindi%20was%20one%20of%20his%20favourites%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20source%20told%20the%20paper.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20also%20claims%20that%20Pant%20lost%20about%2016kgs%20over%20the%20last%20four%20months%2C%20and%20it%20was%20possible%20because%20of%20the%20strict%20sleep%20schedule%20he%20followed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAll%20gadgets%2C%20including%20phones%2C%20iPads%20and%20TVs%20were%20shut%20down%20by%2011%20in%20the%20night.%20He%20had%20to%20have%20eight-nine%20hours%20of%20uninterrupted%20sleep%20to%20get%20back%20to%20rigorous%20training%20next%20morning%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20report%20quoted%20a%20source%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714545660000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fb2kldlig_rishabh-pant-bcci_625x300_01_May_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ft20-world-cup-2024%2Fno-rasmalai-biryani-fried-chicken-how-rishabh-pant-lost-16-kgs-to-make-t20-world-cup-squad-5562903%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Rishabh%20Pant%20followed%20a%20strict%20diet%20and%20sleep%20schedule%20in%20order%20to%20make%20it%20to%20India's%20T20%20World%20Cup%20squad.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22NDTV%20Marathi%20Launched%2C%206th%20News%20Channel%20Of%20The%20Media%20Group%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ENDTV%20has%20today%20launched%20a%20new%20regional%20channel%2C%20NDTV%20Marathi%2C%20to%20provide%20trustworthy%20news%20and%20information%20to%20the%20people%20of%20Maharashtra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20launch%20event%20was%20attended%20by%20Maharashtra%20Chief%20Minister%20Eknath%20Shinde%20and%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20Devendra%20Fadnavis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20network%2C%20which%20runs%20some%20of%20the%20top%20news%20channels%20in%20India%2C%20will%20now%20empower%20the%20'Marathi%20manus'%20(Marathi%20person)%20and%20contribute%20to%20the%20ongoing%20journey%20of%20Maharashtra's%20progress.%20With%20a%20steadfast%20focus%20on%20the%20forward-looking%20ethos%20of%20New%20Maharashtra%2C%20NDTV%20Marathi%20will%20aim%20to%20deliver%20high-quality%20and%20uncluttered%20journalism%2C%20catering%20to%20the%20discerning%20needs%20of%20Maharashtrians.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNDTV%20Marathi%2C%20launched%20on%20Maharashtra%20Day%2C%20is%20the%20sixth%20channel%20from%20the%20NDTV%20network.%20It%20is%20our%20privilege%20to%20serve%20the%20people%20of%20Maharashtra%20with%20meaningful%2C%20accurate%2C%20and%20trustworthy%20news%20and%20analysis%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Sanja