y%20published%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ptinews.com%2Ffact-detail%2FNo--Congress-hasn-t-announced-its-candidates-for-Amethi-and-Raebareli-Lok-Sabha-seats-yet%253B-viral-screenshots-of-press-releases-are-fake%2F1468895%5C%22%3EPTI%20Fact%20Check%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20republished%20by%20NDTV%20as%20part%20of%20the%20Shakti%20Collective.)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714543560000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-11%2Fc9j2ghq_rahul-priyanka_625x300_24_November_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ffact-check-has-congress-announced-rahul-gandhi-as-amethi-candidate-5562788%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20screenshot%20of%20a%20a%20purported%20press%20release%20by%20the%20Congress%2C%20which%20mentions%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20and%20Priyanka%20Gandhi%20Vadra%20as%20party's%20candidates%20for%20the%20prestigious%20Amethi%20and%20Raebareli%20constituencies%20respectively%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%2C%20has%20gone%20viral.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ffact-check-has-congress-announced-rahul-gandhi-as-amethi-candidate-5562788%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ffact-check-has-congress-announced-rahul-gandhi-as-amethi-candidate-5562788%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ffact-check-has-congress-announced-rahul-gandhi-as-amethi-candidate-5562788%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22After%20MI's%20Defeat%20Against%20LSG%2C%20Captain%20Hardik%20Pandya%20Points%20Finger%20At...%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFollowing%20his%20side's%204-wicket%20defeat%20against%20Lucknow%20Super%20Giants%20(LSG)%20in%20the%20Indian%20Premier%20League%20(IPL)%202024%20at%20the%20Ekana%20Cricket%20Stadium%2C%20Mumbai%20Indians%20(MI)%20skipper%20Hardik%20Pandya%20said%20after%20losing%20early%20wickets%20it%20was%20tough%20for%20them%20to%20recover.%20Pandya%20displayed%20a%20sloppy%20performance%20while%20batting%20as%20he%20was%20dismissed%20for%20a%20golden%20duck%20in%20the%20sixth%20over%20of%20the%20first%20inning%20by%20Naveen-ul-Haq.%20However.%20while%20bowling%20the%20skipper%20picked%20up%20two%20wickets%20in%20his%20four-over%20spell%20and%20gave%20away%2026%20runs%20at%20an%20economy%20rate%20of%206.50.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20after%20the%20match%2C%20Pandya%20said%20his%20side%20failed%20to%20see%20the%20ball%20and%20hit.%20He%20added%20that%20there%20have%20been%20lots%20of%20things%20to%20learn%20from%20their%20match%20against%20LSG.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20skipper%20showered%20praise%20on%20Nehal%20Wadhera%20and%20said%20the%2023-year-old%20will%20play%20a%20lot%20of%20IPL%20in%20the%20future%20and%20will%20represent%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWadhera%20scored%2046%20runs%20from%2041%20balls%20at%20a%20strike%20rate%20of%20112.20%20against%20LSG.%20He%20smashed%204%20fours%20and%202%20sixes%20during%20his%20time%20on%20the%20crease.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20losing%20early%20wickets%20is%20tough%20to%20recover%20from%20and%20that's%20what%20we%20couldn't%20do%20it%20(recover)%20today.%20You%20still%20have%20to%20see%20the%20ball%20and%20hit.%20We%20just%20missed%20those%20balls%20and%20got%20out%2C%20that%20has%20been%20the%20kind%20of%20season%20we%20have%20had%20so%20far.%20I%20have%20always%20believed%20that%20you%20will%20be%20up%20and%20you'll%20be%20up%2C%20just%20that%20you%20got%20to%20give%20it%20your%20all.%20A%20lot%20of%20things%20to%20learn%20from%20this%20game.%20It%20has%20been%20fantastic.%20I%20think%20he%20(Wadhera)%20did%20last%20year%20as%20well%2C%20he%20couldn't%20get%20opportunities%20earlier%20(in%20the%20tournament)%20but%20he%20will%20play%20a%20lot%20of%20IPL%20and%20(represent)%20India%20eventually%2C%26quot%3B%20Pandya%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecapping%20the%20match%2C%