nt%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EMumbai%20Indians%20captain%20Hardik%20Pandya%20has%20been%20fined%20Rs%2024%20lakh%20after%20his%20team's%20second%20slow%20over-rate%20offence%20in%20the%20Indian%20Premier%20League%20during%20their%20match%20against%20Lucknow%20Super%20Giants.%20All%20the%20other%20players%2C%20including%20the%20Impact%20Player%2C%20were%20each%20individually%20fined%20either%20Rs%206%20lakh%20or%2025%20per%20cent%20of%20their%20respective%20match%20fees%2C%20whichever%20is%20lesser.%20MI%20lost%20the%20match%20by%20four%20wickets%20at%20the%20Ekana%20Stadium%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMr%20Hardik%20Pandya%2C%20Captain%2C%20Mumbai%20Indians%20has%20been%20fined%20after%20his%20team%20maintained%20a%20slow%20over-rate%20during%20Match%2048%20of%20the%20TATA%20Indian%20Premier%20League%20(IPL)%202024%20against%20Lucknow%20Super%20Giants%20on%20April%2030%2C%202024%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20IPL%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20it%20was%20his%20team's%20second%20offence%20of%20the%20season%20under%20the%20IPL's%20Code%20of%20Conduct%20relating%20to%20minimum%20over-rate%20offences%2C%20Pandya%20was%20fined%20INR%2024%20Lac.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20rest%20of%20the%20members%20of%20the%20Playing%20XI%2C%20including%20the%20Impact%20Player%2C%20were%20each%20individually%20fined%20either%20INR%206%20Lac%20or%2025%20per%20cent%20of%20their%20respective%20match%20fees%2C%20whichever%20is%20lesser%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20the%20match%2C%C2%A0Mumbai%20Indians'%20top-order%20came%20a%20cropper%20as%20they%20stuttered%20to%20a%20below-par%20144%20for%20seven%2C%20riding%20on%20contributions%20from%20Nehal%20Wadhera%20(46)%2C%20Ishan%20Kishan%20(32)%20and%20Tim%20David%20(35%20not%20out).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20reply%2C%20Stoinis%20scored%20a%2045-ball%2062%2C%20studded%20with%20seven%20hits%20to%20the%20fence%20and%20two%20maximums%20but%20once%20he%20was%20gone%20LSG%20survived%20some