3B%20the%20Times%20reported.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EThe%20university%20announced%20later%20in%20the%20evening%20that%20the%20building%20had%20been%20cleared%20of%20protesters%20and%20that%20%26quot%3Bheightened%20activity%26quot%3B%20had%20concluded%2C%20per%20the%20Times.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVideos%20from%20student%20groups%20on%20the%20scene%20show%20protesters%20being%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FNationalSJP%2Fstatus%2F1785482293542301804%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epushed%20off%20campus%20by%20police%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20Washington%20Post%20reported%20that%20some%20police%20entered%20the%20hall%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Feducation%2F2024%2F04%2F30%2Fcolumbia-university-protests-palestine-news%2F%23link-VTS5AUCISFFCRIX7EM65MIQUOU%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eguns%20drawn%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20university%20requested%20that%20students%20shelter%20in%20place%20before%20police%20entered%20the%20campus%20building.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStudent%20groups%20had%20been%20demonstrating%20on%20campus%20for%20days%2C%20setting%20up%20tents%20and%20camping%20out%20at%20the%20Ivy%20League%20University%20to%20protest%20Israel's%20war%20on%20Gaza.%20Demands%20for%20the%20protest%20included%20that%20the%20university%20cut%20financial%20ties%20to%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20university's%20%2413.6%20billion%20endowment%20includes%20investments%20in%20several%20weapons%20manufacturers%20and%20tech%20companies%20that%20do%20business%20with%20the%20Israeli%20government%2C%20which%20the%20student%20coalition%20Columbia%20University%20Apartheid%20Divest%20described%20as%20profiting%20%26quot%3Bfrom%20Israeli%20apartheid%2C%20genocide%2C%20and%20military%20occupation%20of%20Palestine%2C%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnn.com%2F2024%2F04%2F27%2Fbusiness%2Fcolumbia-history-divestment-student-protests%2Findex.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECNN%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported.%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EOn%20Tuesday%2C%20protesters%20entered%20Hamilton%20Hall%2C%20a%20humanities%20building%20on%20the%20university's%20Morningside%20Heights%20campus%2C%20and%20barricaded%20themselves%20indoors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EColumbia%20announced%20in%20a%20statement%20that%20students%20who%20occupied%20Hamilton%20Hall%20will%20face%20expulsion%2C%20while%20students%20who%20participated%20in%20encampments%20and%20refused%20to%20leave%20at%20the%20university's%20direction%20will%20face%20suspension.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EColumbia%20University%2C%20Columbia%20Students%20for%20Justice%20in%20Palestine%2C%20and%20the%20NYPD%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20requests%20for%20comment%20from%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EColumbia%20released%20a%20statement%20Tuesday%20evening%20saying%20it%20gave%20the%20NYPD%20the%20green%20light%20to%20enter%20the%20campus%20and%20disperse%20student%20protesters.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20regret%20that%20protesters%20have%20chosen%20to%20escalate%20the%20situation%20through%20their%20actions%2C%26quot%3B%20adding%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20made%20the%20decision%2C%20early%20in%20the%20morning%2C%20that%20this%20was%20a%20law%20enforcement%20matter%2C%20and%20that%20the%20NYPD%20were%20best%20positioned%20to%20determine%20and%20execute%20an%20appropriate%20response.%26quot%3B%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EThe%20school%20also%20said%20the%20protesters%20had%20been%20%26quot%3Bled%20by%20individuals%20who%20are%20not%20affiliated%20with%20the%20University.%26quot%3B%3Cstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3EIn%20a%20live%20broadcast%2C%20reporters%20at%20Columbia%20student%20news%20station%20WKCR%20noted%20that%20only%20Columbia%20ID%20holders%20could%20be%20on%20campus%20and%20questioned%20the%20university's%20security.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EColumbia's%20President%20Minouche%20Shafik%20requested%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpublicsafety.columbia.edu%2Fnews%2Fletter-nypd-apr-30%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ein%20a%20letter%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20the%20NYPD%20that%20the%20police%20maintain%20a%20presence%20on%20campus%20until%20May%2017%20to%20shut%20down%20any%20future%20encampments.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EAt%20least%20two%20New%20York%20representatives%20spoke%20out%20against%20Columbia's%20decision%20to%20let%20NYPD%20forcibly%20remove%20students%20from%20Hamilton%20Hall.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERep.%20Jamaal%20Bowman%20said%20he%20was%20%26quot%3Boutraged%20by%20the%20level%20of%20police%20presence%20called%20upon%20nonviolent%20student%20protestors%26quot%3B%20at%20Columbia%20and%20The%20City%20College%20of%20New%20York%20%E2%80%94%20another%20New%20York%20institution%20with%20students%20staging%20a%20similar%20encampment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20an%20educator%20who%20has%20first%20hand%20experience%20with%20the%20over-policing%20of%20our%20schools%2C%20this%20is%20personal%20to%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20Bowman%20posted%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fplatform.twitter.com%2Fwidgets.js%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EI%20am%20outraged%20by%20the%20level%20of%20police%20presence%20called%20upon%20nonviolent%20student%20protestors%20on%20Columbia%20and%20CCNY%E2%80%99s%20campuses.%20As%20an%20educator%20who%20has%20first%20hand%20experience%20with%20the%20over-policing%20of%20our%20schools%2C%20this%20is%20personal%20to%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%E2%80%94%20Congressman%20Jamaal%20Bowman%20(%40RepBowman)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FRepBowman%2Fstatus%2F1785483005890355359%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EMay%201%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3ERep.%20Alexandria%20Ocasio-Cortez%20said%20that%20if%20students%20were%20hurt%20by%20the%20NYPD%2C%20the%20responsibility%20would%20fall%20on%20the%20university%20president%20and%20New%20York%20City%20Mayor%20Eric%20Adams%2C%20who%20expressed%