2%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Google%20CEO%20Sundar%20Pichai%20Nears%20Billionaire%20Status%20Amid%20AI%20Boom%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAlphabet%20Inc.%20Chief%20Executive%20Officer%20Sundar%20Pichai%20is%20on%20the%20cusp%20of%20achieving%20a%20rare%20milestone%20for%20a%20non-founder%20tech%20executive%3A%20a%2010-figure%20fortune.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20Pichai%2C%2051%2C%20became%20CEO%20of%20Google%20in%202015%2C%20the%20stock%20has%20surged%20more%20than%20400%25%2C%20significantly%20outperforming%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20and%20Nasdaq%20over%20the%20same%20period.%20It%20hit%20a%20fresh%20record%20Friday%20after%20the%20company's%20first-quarter%20earnings%20beat%20expectations%2C%20boosted%20by%20AI-driven%20growth%20in%20its%20cloud%20computing%20unit.%20It%20also%20introduced%20a%20dividend%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%20its%20history.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20rally%2C%20alongside%20hefty%20stock%20awards%20that%20have%20made%20him%20one%20of%20the%20world's%20highest-paid%20executives%2C%20has%20boosted%20Pichai's%20fortune%20to%20nearly%20%241%20billion%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Bloomberg%20Billionaires%20Index.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20Google%20spokesperson%20declined%20to%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt's%20a%20remarkable%20rise%20for%20the%20native%20of%20Chennai%2C%20India%2C%20who%20grew%20up%20in%20a%20two-room%20apartment%20where%20he%20and%20his%20younger%20brother%20slept%20on%20the%20living%20room%20floor.%20During%20much%20of%20his%20childhood%2C%20the%20Pichais%20didn't%20have%20a%20television%20or%20a%20car%2C%20he%20has%20said%20in%20interviews.%20At%20times%2C%20they%20didn't%20even%20have%20running%20water.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20family%20got%20their%20first%20rotary%20telephone%20when%20he%20was%2012%2C%20which%20he%20said%20introduced%20him%20to%20the%20conveniences%20of%20technology.%20That%2C%20along%20with%20a%20healthy%20curiosity%20about%20his%20father's%20job%20as%20an%20electrical%20engineer%20for%20the%20British%20conglomerate%20GEC%2C%20attracted%20the%20young%20Pichai%20to%20the%20tech%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20excelled%20at%20school%2C%20eventually%20landing%20a%20spot%20at%20the%20prestigious%20Indian%20Institute%20of%20Technology%20in%20Kharagpur%2C%20where%20he%20studied%20engineering.%20When%20he%20won%20a%20scholarship%20to%20Stanford%20University%2C%20his%20father%20withdrew%20%241%2C000%20from%20the%20family's%20savings%20-%20more%20than%20his%20annual%20salary%20-%20to%20cover%20the%20cost%20of%20Pichai's%20plane%20ticket%20and%20other%20expenses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20dad%20and%20mom%20did%20what%20a%20lot%20of%20parents%20did%20at%20the%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20Pichai%20said%20in%20a%202014%20interview.%20%26quot%3BThey%20sacrificed%20a%20lot%20of%20their%20life%20and%20used%20a%20lot%20of%20their%20disposable%20income%20to%20make%20sure%20their%20children%20were%20educated.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20earning%20another%20advanced%20degree%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Pennsylvania's%20Wharton%20School%20and%20a%20stint%20as%20a%20consultant%20at%20McKinsey%2C%20he%20joined%20Google%20in%202004%20as%20a%20product%20manager%2C%20leading%20the%20development%20of%20major%20projects%20like%20the%20Google%20Toolbar%20and%20Google%20Chrome.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E'Great%20Facilitator'%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPichai's%20humility%20and%20ability%20to%20build%20consensus%20emerged%20early%20on%2C%20said%20Keval%20Desai%2C%20who%20worked%20with%20him%20during%20his%20first%20years%20at%20Google.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe's%20not%20looking%20to%20be%20the%20most%20dominant%20voice%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Desai%2C%20who%20is%20now%20a%20founder%20and%20managing%20director%20at%20Shakti%2C%20a%20San%20Francisco-based%20venture%20capital%20firm.%20%26quot%3BHe's%20very%20comfortable%20in%20his%20own%20skin.%20It%20allowed%20him%20very%20early%20on%20to%20be%20a%20great%20facilitator%20across%20these%20strong%2C%20opinionated%20people.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPichai%20was%20selected%20in%202015%20by%20co-founder%20Larry%20Page%20to%20be%20Google's%20CEO%2C%20while%20Page%20became%20CEO%20of%20newly%20formed%20holding%20company%20Alphabet.%20Pichai%20took%20over%20that%20role%20as%20well%20in%202019%20when%20Page%20and%20co-founder%20Sergey%20Brin%20-%20two%20of%20the%2010%20richest%20people%20in%20the%20world%2C%20according%20to%20Bloomberg's%20wealth%20index%20-%20stepped%20back%20from%20day-to-day%20management.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20no%20one%20that%20we%20have%20relied%20on%20more%20since%20Alphabet%20was%20founded%2C%20and%20no%20better%20person%20to%20lead%20Google%20and%20Alphabet%20into%20the%20future%2C%26quot%3B%20Brin%20and%20Page%2C%20who%20combined%20have%20a%20net%20worth%20of%20almost%20%24300%20billion%2C%20said%20of%20Pichai%20in%20a%202019%20letter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20time%20as%20CEO%2C%20Pichai%20has%20overseen%20a%20major%20expansion%20of%20the%20company's%20product%20line%20with%20the%20addition%20of%20Google%20Assistant%2C%20Google%20Home%2C%20Google%20Pixel%2C%20Google%20Workspace%20and%20more.%20He%20was%20also%20an%20early%20adopter%20of%20artificial%20intelligence%2C%20calling%20it%20a%20%26quot%3Bonce-in-a-generation%20opportunity.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Alphabet%20has%20been%20criticized%20for%20its%20AI%20offerings%20and%20some%20investors%20have%20questioned%20its%20ability%20to%20compete%20with%20OpenAI%2C%20last%20week's%20earnings%20provided%20reassurance%20that%20its%20spending%20on%20the%20technology%20is%20starting%20to%20pay%20off.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPichai's%20net%20worth%20includes%20%24424%20million%20in%20current%20shareholdings%20as%20well%20as%20roughly%20%24600%20million%20from%20share%20sales%20since%20he%20became%20CEO.%20Bloomberg's%20wealth%20index%20assumes%20those%20sales%20were%20taxed%20and%20reinvested%20in%20the%20stock%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPichai's%20status%20as%20a%20near-billionaire%20is%20a%20reminder%20of%20the%20value%20that%20he%20has%20created%20during%20his%20time%20at%20the%20helm%20of%20Google%2C%20Desai%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20it%20says%20to%20me%20is%20first%20and%20foremost%20that%20he%20has%20done%20right%20by%20shareholders%2C%26quot%3B%20Desai%20said.%20%26quot%3BHe's%20benefited%20because%20Google's%20stock%20has%20done%20really%20well.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714536420000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-01%2Ff8uj6gqo_sundar-pichai-bloomberg_625x300_24_January_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fgoogle-ceo-sundar-pichai-nears-billionaire-status-amid-ai-boom-5562136%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Alphabet%20Inc.%20Chief%20Executive%20Officer%20Sundar%20Pichai%20is%20on%20the%20cusp%20of%20achieving%20a%20rare%20milestone%20for%20a%20non-founder%20tech%20executive%3A%20a%2010-figure%20fortune.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fgoogle-ceo-sundar-pichai-nears-billionaire-status-amid-ai-boom-5562136%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fgoogle-ceo-sundar-pichai-nears-billionaire-status-amid-ai-boom-5562136%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fgoogle-ceo-sundar-pichai-nears-billionaire-status-amid-ai-boom-5562136%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22US%20Reacts%20To%20Washington%20Post's%20India%20Claim%20In%20Terrorist%20Pannun%20Killing%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20United%20States%20is%20%26quot%3Bregularly%20working%26quot%3B%20with%20India%20in%20its%20investigation%20into%20the%20allegations%20related%20to%20the%20plot%20to%20assassinate%20Khalistani%20t