esperson%20Randhir%20Jaiswal%20on%20Tuesday%20slammed%20the%20report%20by%20the%20US%20daily.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20report%20in%20question%20makes%20unwarranted%20and%20unsubstantiated%20imputations%20on%20a%20serious%20matter%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20in%20New%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Jaiswal%20said%20a%20high-level%20inquiry%20committee%20set%20up%20by%20New%20Delhi%20to%20look%20into%20inputs%20provided%20by%20the%20US%20on%20the%20alleged%20plot%20was%20still%20probing%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20an%20ongoing%20investigation%20of%20the%20high-level%20committee%20set%20up%20by%20the%20Government%20of%20India%20to%20look%20into%20the%20security%20concerns%20shared%20by%20the%20US%20government%20on%20networks%20of%20organised%20criminals%2C%20terrorists%20and%20others%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSpeculative%20and%20irresponsible%20comments%20on%20it%20are%20not%20helpful%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Jaiswal%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20November%20last%20year%2C%20US%20federal%20prosecutors%20charged%20Indian%20national%20Nikhil%20Gupta%20with%20working%20with%20an%20Indian%20government%20employee%20in%20the%20foiled%20plot%20to%20kill%20Pannun.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPannun%2C%20wanted%20in%20India%20on%20terror%20charges%2C%20holds%20dual%20citizenship%20of%20the%20US%20and%20Canada.%20He%20has%20been%20designated%20as%20a%20terrorist%20by%20the%20Union%20home%20ministry%20under%20the%20anti-terror%20law%20Unlawful%20Activities%20(Prevention)%20Act.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20allegations%20about%20the%20failed%20plot%20to%20kill%20Pannun%20came%20to%20the%20fore%20weeks%20after%20Canadian%20Prime%20Minister%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Flooking-to-work-constructively-with-indian-govt-canadian-pm-on-nijjars-killing-5323537%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJustin%20Trudeau%3C%2Fa%3E%20claimed%20in%20September%20last%20year%20of%20a%20%26quot%3Bpotential%26