%3B%20Musk%20told%20Lemon%20about%20his%20political%20contributions.%20%26quot%3BI%20may%2C%20in%20the%20final%20stretch%2C%20endorse%20a%20candidate%2C%20but%20I%20don't%20know%20yet.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-david-sacks-dinner-anti-biden-hollywood-hills-2024-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714535881000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F658a40721c5c7b8c9a0bee4b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-david-sacks-dinner-anti-biden-hollywood-hills-2024-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Elon%20Musk%20hosted%20a%20dinner%20for%20billionaires%20that%20got%20political%2C%20Puck%20reported%2C%20and%20attendees%20discussed%20their%20distrust%20of%20Democrats%20like%20Joe%20Biden.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ktangalakislippert%40businessinsider.com%20(Katherine%20Tangalakis-Lippert)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A12%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-david-sacks-dinner-anti-biden-hollywood-hills-2024-4%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Godrej%20Family%20Announces%20Split%20After%20127%20Years%3A%20Who%20Gets%20What%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20founding%20family%20of%20127-year-old%20Godrej%20Group%2C%20which%20spans%20from%20soaps%20and%20home%20appliances%20to%20real%20estate%2C%20has%20reached%20an%20agreement%20to%20split%20the%20conglomerate%2C%20with%20Adi%20Godrej%20and%20his%20brother%20Nadir%20keeping%20Godrej%20Industries%20that%20has%20five%20listed%20firms%2C%20while%20cousins%20Jamshyd%20and%20Smita%20getting%20unlisted%20Godrej%20%26amp%3B%20Boyce%20and%20its%20affiliates%20as%20well%20as%20a%20land%20bank%2C%20including%20prime%20property%20in%20Mumbai.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20group%20has%20been%20split%20between%20two%20branches%20of%20the%20founding%20family%2C%20with%20Adi%20Godrej%20(82)%20and%20his%20brother%20Nadir%20(73)%20on%20one%20side%20and%20their%20cousins%20Jamshyd%20Godrej%20(75)%20and%20Smita%20Godrej%20Crishna%20(74)%20on%20the%20other%2C%20according%20to%20a%20statement%20issued%20by%20the%20group.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGodrej%20Enterprises%20Group%20--%20comprising%20Godrej%20%26amp%3B%20Boyce%20and%20its%20affiliates%20that%20have%20a%20presence%20across%20multiple%20industries%20spanning%20aerospace%20and%20aviation%20to%20defence%2C%20furniture%20and%20IT%20software%20--%20will%20be%20controlled%20by%20Jamshyd%20Godrej%20as%20chairperson%20and%20managing%20director.%20His%20sister%20Smita's%20daughter%20Nyrika%20Holkar%2C%2042%2C%20will%20be%20the%20executive%20director.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20families%20will%20control%20this%20arm%20that%20also%20will%20hold%20the%20land%20bank%2C%20including%203%2C400%20acres%20of%20prime%20land%20in%20Mumbai.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGodrej%20Industries%20Group%20--%20which%20includes%20the%20listed%20companies%20-%20Godrej%20Industries%2C%20Godrej%20Consumer%20Products%2C%20Godrej%20Properties%2C%20Godrej%20Agrovet%20and%20Astec%20Lifesciences%20--%20will%20have%20Nadir%20Godrej%20as%20chairperson%20and%20will%20be%20controlled%20by%20Adi%2C%20Nadir%20and%20their%20immediate%20families.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPirojsha%20Godrej%2C%2042%2C%20son%20of%20Adi%2C%20will%20be%20the%20executive%20vice%20chairperson%20of%20GIG%20and%20will%20succeed%20Nadir%20as%20the%20chairperson%20in%20August%202026%2C%20the%20statement%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20statement%2C%20the%20Godrej%20family%20termed%20the%20split%20as%20%26quot%3Ban%20ownership%20realignment%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20shareholdings%20in%20the%20Godrej%20companies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20realignment%20has%20been%20arrived%20at%20in%20a%20respectful%20and%20mindful%20way%20to%20maintain%20harmony%20and%20to%20better%20align%20ownership%20in%20acknowledgement%20of%20the%20differing%20visions%20of%20the%20Godrej%20family%20members%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20will%20help%20maximize%20strategic%20direction%2C%20focus%2C%20and%20agility%2C%20and%20will%20accelerate%20the%20process%20of%20creating%20long-term%20value%20for%20shareholders%20and%20all%20other%20stakeholders.%26quot%3B%20Both%20Groups%20will%20continue%20to%20use%20the%20Godrej%20brand%20and%20are%20committed%20to%20growing%20and%20strengthening%20their%20shared%20heritage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELawyer-turned-serial%20entrepreneur%20Ardeshir%20Godrej%20and%20his%20brother%20in%201897%20succeeded%20at%20locksmithing%20after%20failed%20ventures%20into%20hand-fashioned%20medical%20devices.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArdeshir%20did%20not%20have%20any%20children%2C%20and%20so%20the%20group%20was%20inherited%20by%20his%20younger%20brother%20Pirojsha.%20Pirojsha%20had%20four%20children%20-%20Sohrab%2C%20Dosa%2C%20Burjor%20and%20Naval.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20years%2C%20the%20helm%20of%20the%20group%20came%20to%20the%20children%20of%20Burjor%20(Adi%20and%20Nadir)%20and%20Naval%20(Jamshyd%20and%20Smita)%20as%20Sohrab%20had%20no%20children%20while%20Dosa%20had%20one%20child%20Rishad%2C%20who%20had%20no%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20enable%20the%20split%2C%20the%20two%20sides%20quit%20the%20boards%20of%20companies%20in%20rival%20camps.%20So%2C%20Adi%20and%20Nadir%20Godrej%20resigned%20from%20the%20Godrej%20%26amp%3B%20Boyce%20Board%2C%20while%20Jamshyd%20Godrej%20left%20his%20seat%20on%20the%20boards%20of%20GCPL%20and%20Godrej%20Properties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnconfirmed%20reports%20say%20Adi%20and%20Nadir%20Godrej%20will%20divest%20their%20stakes%20in%20Godrej%20%26amp%3B%20Boyce%20to%20the%20other%20branch.%20Jamshyd%20Godrej%20and%20his%20side%20of%20the%20family%20will%20transfer%20interests%20in%20Godrej%20Consumer%20Products%20(GCPL)%20and%20Godrej%20Properties%20to%20their%20cousins%20through%20a%20family%20arrangement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReal%20estate%20worth%20crores%20of%20rupees%2C%20mostly%20in%20prime%20land%20in%20Mumbai%20suburbs%2C%20will%20remain%20under%20Godrej%20%26amp%3B%20Boyce%20(G%26amp%3BB)%2C%20and%20a%20separate%20agreement%20will%20be%20worked%20out%20to%20govern%20the%20ownership%20rights.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20owns%203%2C400%20acres%20of%20land%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20including%20a%203%2C000-acre%20parcel%20in%20Vikhroli%2C%20Mumbai.%20The%20Vikhroli%20land%20by%20some%20estimates%20has%20a%20development%20potential%20of%20over%20Rs%201%20lakh%20crore.%20It%20can%20develop%201%2C000%20acres%2C%20while%20about%201%2C750%20acres%20are%20covered%20with%20mangroves%20and%20is%20the%20destination%20of%20rare%20plants%20and%20birds.%20About%20300%20acres%20of%20land%20have%20already%20been%20encroached%20upon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Vikhroli%20property%20was%20bought%20by%20Pirojsha%20at%20a%20public%20auction%20from%20the%20Bombay%20High%20Court%20receiver%20in%201941-42.%20It%20was%20previously%20owned%20by%20a%20Parsi%20merchant%20Framjee%20Banaji%2C%20who%20bought%20it%20from%20the%20East%20India%20Company%20in%20the%201830s.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdi%20is%20currently%20chairman%20of%20Godrej%20Group.%20His%20brother%20Nadir%20is%20chairman%20of%20Godrej%20Industries%20and%20Godrej%20Agrovet.%20Their%20cousin%20Jamshyd%20is%20chairman%20of%20the%20unlisted%20Godrej%20%26amp%3B%20Boyce%20Manufacturing%20company.%20His%20sister%20Smita%20Crishna%20and%20Rishad%20Godrej%20also%20hold%20a%20stake%20in%20Godrej%20%26amp%3B%20Boyce%2C%20which%20owns%20most%20of%20the%20property%20in%20Vikhroli.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20couple%20of%20years%20back%2C%20Jamshyd%20roped%20in%20investment%20banker%20Nimesh%20Kampani%20and%20lawyer%20Zia%20Mody%20to%20advise%20him%20on%20separating%20the%20land%20ownership.%20Kotak%20Mahindra%20Bank's%20Uday%20Kotak%20and%20Cyril%20Shroff%20of%20legal%20firm%20Cyril%20Amarchand%20Mangaldas%20were%20assisting%20Adi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20statement%2C%20the%20realignment%20will%20be%20implemented%20after%20the%20relevant%20regulatory%20approvals%20have%20been%20obtained.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGodrej%20Enterprises%20Group%20(GEG)%20comprises%20Godrej%20%26amp%3B%20Boyce%20(G%26amp%3BB)%20and%20its%20affiliates%2C%20which%20have%20a%20presence%20across%20multiple%20industries%20spanning%20aerospace%2C%20aviation%2C%20defence%2C%20engines%20and%20motors%2C%20energy%2C%20security%2C%20building%20materials%2C%20construction%2C%20green%20building%20consulting%2C%20EPC%20services%2C%20intralogistics%2C%20healthcare%20equipment%2C%20durables%2C%20furniture%2C%20interior%20design%2C%20architectural%20fittings%2C%20IT%2C%20software%20as%20well%20as%20infrastructure%20solutions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20group%20will%20now%20be%20controlled%20by%20Jamshyd%20Godrej%2C%20chairperson%20and%20managing%20director%2C%20Nyrika%20Holkar%2C%20Executive%20Director%2C%20and%20their%20immediate%20families%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGodrej%20Industries%20Group%20(GIG)%2C%20which%20includes%20the%20listed%20companies%2C%20Godrej%20Industries%2C%20Godrej%20Consumer%20Products%2C%20Godrej%20Properties%2C%20Godrej%20Agrovet%20and%20Astec%20Lifesciences%20will%20have%20Nadir%20Godrej%20as%20Chairperson%20and%20will%20be%20controlled%20by%20Adi%20Godrej%2C%20Nadir%20Godrej%2C%20and%20their%20immediate%20families.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPirojsha%20Godrej%20will%20be%20the%20Executive%20Vice%20Chairperson%20of%20GIG%20and%20will%20succeed%20Nadir%20Godrej%20as%20the%20Chairperson%20in%20August%202026%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECommenting%20on%20the%20future%20outlook%2C%20Jamshyd%20Godrej%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BSince%201897%2C%20Godrej%20%26amp%3B%20Boyce%20has%20always%20been%20driven%20by%20the%20strong%20purpose%20of%20nation%20building.%20With%20this%20future-facing%20family%20agreement%20now%20in%20place%2C%20we%20can%20further%20drive%20our%20growth%20aspirations%20with%20fewer%20complexities%