a%20tourist%20trap%2C%20almost%2070%25%20said%20their%20visit%20to%20a%20tourist%20trap%20diminished%20their%20overall%20enjoyment%20of%20their%20trip.%20Only%20around%2013%25%20said%20it%20actually%20added%20enjoyment%20to%20their%20trip.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20why%20do%20Americans%20keep%20visiting%20these%20places%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20would%20appear%20social%20factors%20are%20largely%20to%20blame.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20third%20of%20respondents%20said%20they%20went%20because%20their%20family%20or%20friends%20wanted%20to%20go%20(though%20you%20have%20to%20wonder%20if%20said%20family%20or%20friends%20would%20give%20the%20same%20reason)%2C%20while%20nearly%2020%25%20said%20they%20went%20because%20it%20was%20highly%20recommended.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20reasons%20cited%20included%20curiosity%20or%20personal%20interest%2C%20the%20site%20being%20considered%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffamous-landmarks-construction-2018-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elandmark%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20that%20it%20was%20part%20of%20a%20tour%20package.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20offered%20advice%20on%20how%20to%20avoid%20falling%20into%20a%20tourist%20trap%2C%20the%20survey%20respondents%20said%20the%20most%20helpful%20tip%20was%20to%20%26quot%3Bvisit%20well-known%20landmarks%2C%20but%20don't%20make%20them%20the%20sole%20focus%20of%20your%20trip.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAvoiding%20so-called%20tourist%20traps%2C%20or%20at%20least%20spending%20less%20time%20at%20them%2C%20could%20also%20help%20curb%20the%20impacts%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fovertourism-measures-limit-tourism-going-to-increase-venice-amsterdam-rome-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eovertourism%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETourism%20experts%20previously%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20spreading%20out%20tourists%20who%20otherwise%20congregate%20at%20the%20same%20places%20at%20the%20exact%20same%20times%20can%20help%20destinations%20mana