0her%20daughter%20and%20the%20emotional%20strain%20it%20caused%20her.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20could%20see%20her%20only%20during%20certain%20times%20of%20the%20day%20when%20I%20was%20called%20in%20to%20breastfeed%20her.%20Just%20seeing%20this%20tiny%20human%20with%20so%20many%20devices%20attached%20to%20her%20was%20harrowing%3B%20to%20say%20the%20least%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20neighbouring%20state%20of%20Karnataka%2C%20Manoj%20Sanker%20saw%20his%20parents%20go%20through%20a%20similar%20trial%20when%20their%20second%20son%20was%20born%20premature.%20He%20recounts%20seeing%20his%20middle%20class%20family%20going%20above%20and%20beyond%20to%20ensure%20that%20he%20got%20the%20best%20treatment.%20Years%20later%2C%20when%2032-year-old%20Manoj%20had%20to%20think%20of%20a%20startup%20idea%20in%20healthcare%2C%20neonatal%20care%20was%20his%20first%20choice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPratyusha%20Pareddy%20hails%20from%20a%20family%20of%20doctors%20and%20grew%20up%20in%20a%20household%20where%20healthcare%20was%20dinner%20table%20conversation.%20After%20completing%20her%20engineering%2C%20the%2037-year-old%20did%20a%20masters%20degree%20in%20Industrial%20and%20Product%20Design%20from%20the%20National%20Institute%20of%20Design.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20a%20project%20at%20NID%2C%20she%20learnt%20about%20how%20design%20could%20transcend%20beyond%20aesthetics%20and%20be%20used%20to%20create%20a%20difference.%20She%20wanted%20to%20use%20her%20designs%20to%20create%20impact%20and%20improve%20lives%20at%20the%20grassroot%20level.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20duo%20shared%20a%20common%20vision%20of%20using%20technology%20and%20design%20to%20build%20solutions%20for%20the%20most%20vulnerable%20population%2C%20i.e.%20babies.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201280px)%20100vw%2C%201280px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2F