ing-plants-flowers-during-winter-cold-season-in-india-gardening-tips%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eadorns%20yellow%20flowers%3C%2Fa%3E%20every%20season.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20tree%20on%20Estate%20Paathiri%20existed%20on%20the%20land%20years%20before%20we%20found%20it%2C%20and%20I%20wanted%20to%20ensure%20that%20it%20stays%20there%20for%20a%20long%20time%20to%20come.%20It%20passes%20right%20through%20the%20master%20bedroom%20of%20the%20home%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares%20in%20a%20conversation%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EInspiration%20comes%20from%20home%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELocated%20in%20Wayanad%2C%20Kerala%2C%20Estate%20Paathiri%20is%20the%20perfect%20place%20to%20seek%20solace.%20While%20the%20world%20bustles%20with%20noises%2C%20here%20you%20will%20wake%20up%20to%20the%20sounds%20of%20birds%20chirping%20in%20the%20morning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20reason%20and%20inspiration%20for%20nature%20being%20a%20recurring%20theme%20in%20George%E2%80%99s%20work%20goes%20back%20to%20his%20childhood.%20Born%20in%20Coorg%2C%20George%20says%20he%20grew%20up%20around%20nature.%20%E2%80%9CI%20went%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F197644%2Flifestyle-order-ooty-chocolates-online-handmade-organic-empower-women-tamil-nadu%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20school%20in%20Ooty%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20covered%20with%20forest%20all%20around.%20It%20was%20this%20proximity%20to%20nature%20that%20made%20me%20feel%20one%20with%20it.%20Now%20I%20believe%20that%20there%20is%20no%20material%20or%20design%20that%20can%20be%20superior%20to%20what%20nature%20has%20to%20offer%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECalling%20the%20place%20a%20natural%20oasis%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CIn%20our%20earlier%20projects%20we%20have%20always%20ensured%20that%20the%20place%20is%20full%20of%20trees%20and%20greenery%20but%20this%20particular%20one%20is%20unique.%20Its%20focal%20point%20is%20a%20tree%20itself%2C%20which%20is%20very%20fascinating.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20green%20haven%20is%20a%20home%20for%20the%20current%20owners%20of%20the%20property%20%E2%80%94%20Cherian%20T%20Ramapuram%20and%20his%20family.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20we%20work%20on%20a%20project%2C%20we%20try%20to%20be%20in%20sync%20with%20our%20clients%E2%80%99%20requirements.%20While%20most%20of%20the%20ideas%20for%20the%20home%20were%20ours%2C%20the%20client%20always%20resonated%20with%20what%20we%20presented%20to%20them.%20They%20were%20very%20keen%20on%20preserving%20the%20nature%20around%20the%20property%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20George.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fhome-1-1713879946.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20estate%20is%20named%20after%20a%20decades-old%20tree%20that%20stands%20on%20the%20property.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fhome-1-1713879946.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fhome-1-1713879946-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fhome-1-1713879946-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fhome-1-1713879946-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fhome-1-1713879946-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-348084%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20estate%20is%20named%20after%20a%20decades-old%20tree%20that%20stands%20on%20the%20property.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20a%20green%20signal%20from%20the%20owners%2C%20Georg